message.entry: Incorrect number of input arguments. ''{0}'' must be followed by a corresponding value.
''AggregationVariables'' parameter is supported only when second argument is ''sum'' or ''mean''.
''AggregationVariables'' function handle must return a logical scalar.
''PickVariable'' parameter is supported only when second input is ''min'' or ''max''.
''PickVariable'' value must be an index between 2 and the number of variables in the Edges table, or a variable name from the Edges table (other than ''EndNodes'').
Input graph has no edge weights. Add edge weights to the graph or specify ''{0}'' parameter.
Undefined function ''{0}'' for edge variable ''{1}'' of type {2}.
''PickVariable'' value must be an edge variable that is a column vector.
